# CoverCredit — Netlify Redirects
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Proxy /og/:slug to backend — keeps covercredit.in in the URL
# WhatsApp/Facebook crawlers hit this URL and get correct OG tags
# Humans get instantly redirected to the blog post by the backend
/og/*   https://api.covercredit.in/og/:splat   200

# All other routes — SPA fallback
/*      /index.html     200
